cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR 

This paper primarily deals with vision-based navigation of autonomous vehicles, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) categories. The study also involves the use of deep neural networks (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) to develop an approach for mitigating the adverse effects of hazardous environments on autonomous vehicles. Additionally, the paper discusses the potential for compromising the DNN-based system, which falls under the computer security (cs.CR) category.
